> Hydras:
>
> Hydras left the place and starte to walk towards the exit, he opened 
> his comlink and said "here is hydras, what's going on outside? I'll 
> join to party right now" 

Myrmidon continued to float in midair, watching Malice as the question
came through. "Your intruder appears to be the servant of Megatron?!" 

Myrmidon's optics turned to regard the image again as he continued to
speak with Hydras, "They challenge your authority."

He closed the channel and waited, surprised at his own reaction to all
of this. Typically by now he would have already been on the attack, but
something held him back . . .

Preston
(Myrmidon)
